        |рассчитывать на:

      .finances-section__content
        .finances-section__image-container
          .finances-section__image
            img(src="images/finances-image.jpg" loading="lazy" alt="image" width="512" height="531").d-block.border-r-20
          .finances-section__image-decor
            img(src="images/finances-decor.png" loading="lazy" alt="image" width="467" height="641").d-block.border-r-20
